Package cz.muni.fi.pb162.project.db

Interface Summary
Connection This interface represents connection established with a remote host.
Connector This interface handles connection to the remote host.
Storage This interface handles the persistent storage of graphical objects.
 

Class Summary
MyStorage Storing graphical objects to a remote database server.
UnrealibleConnector This class represents a simple fake Connector simulating unrealible connection to remote host (the connection is unsuccessul until several attempts).
 

Exception Summary
CannotStoreException Exception for error when there was succeeded to establish a connection, but failed to save data for several attempts.
DbException Exception for error when saving data to a remote server.
DbUnreachableException Exception for error when connecting to the remote database server.
